communication internship office department of communication stanford university comm stanford edu stanford homepage comm people programs research courses internships mcclatchy contact internship office what does the internship office do i we publicize internship opportunities we provide internship and job listings and other resources for students if you are an employer and have information about an internship opportunity that you would like us to send out to our email lists please fill out the following web form employer submission form ii we coordinate the rebele internship fund stanford university students have a unique opportunity to receive stipends for internships at qualifying weekly and daily newspapers through the generosity of a stanford alumnus rowland rebele and his wife pat rebele the rebeles established the fund to provide extra support and encouragement both to newspapers and interns in the form of supplementary stipends iii we accept applications for the daniel pearl memorial journalism internship the daniel pearl memorial journalism internship is awarded annually to an outstanding stanford student journalist and commemorates the work of daniel pearl a stanford graduate who was kidnapped and murdered while working as a wall street journal foreign correspondent in pakistan in 2002 internship office job & internship postings rebele internship fund daniel pearl journalism internship resources cnpa internship grants application advice information department of communication building 120 room 110 450 serra mall stanford university stanford ca 94305 2050 t 650.723 1941 f 650.725 2472 comm inforequest lists stanford edu questions contact student services search communication comm stanford edu stanford university
